                   at the DW to induce the dipolar exciton confinement via the
                   Stark effect. Spatially resolved photoluminescence (PL)
                   spectroscopy reveals the emergence of narrow emission lines
                   redshifted from the MoSe$_2$ neutral exciton by up to
