               layered crystals such as graphene and MoS2. However, polarization
               sensitivity within such a photodetector remains elusive. Here, we
               demonstrate a broadband photodetector using a layered black
               phosphorus transistor that is polarization-sensitive over a
               bandwidth from ∼400 nm to 3,750 nm. The polarization sensitivity
