               many-body interactions provides new tools for accessing
               few-polariton quantum correlations.",
  month     =  jun,
  year      =  2023,
  language  = "en"
}

@ARTICLE{Wei2023-by,
  title     = "Charged biexciton polaritons sustaining strong nonlinearity in
