               Kenji and Eda, Goki and Pereira, Vitor M and Gomes, José C V",
  journal   = "Sci. Rep.",
  publisher = "Nature Publishing Group",
  volume    =  8,
  number    =  1,
  pages     =  10035,
  abstract  = "We report the first detailed characterization of the sheet
               third-harmonic optical susceptibility, χ(3)s, of tungsten
               diselenide (WSe2). With a home-built multiphoton microscope setup
               developed to study harmonics generation, we map the second and
               third-harmonic intensities as a function of position in the
               sample, pump power and polarization angle, for single- and
               few-layers flakes of WSe2. We register a value of |χ(3)s| ≈ 0.9 ×
               10-28 m3 V-2 at a fundamental excitation frequency of ℏω = 0.8
               eV, which is comparable in magnitude to the third-harmonic
