               pairs produced by spontaneous parametric down-conversion (SPDC)
               in entanglement transfer process and quantum computing. The
               simplicity of SPDC entanglement relative to other quantum
               phenomena is first emphasized by developing a complete classical
               theory of the photon-crystal interactions characteristic of SPDC.
               The methods of achieving polarization superposition via the
               Type-I and Type-II SPDC are described. A combination of
